Writes:  3 requests in 3 batches (9216 bytes)
SQL Pods CPU seconds:  3.80
PGWire egress:  0 bytes
ExternalIO egress: 0 bytes
ExternalIO ingress: 0 bytes

# Test egress.
pgwire-egress
12345
----

advance
40s
----
00:04:10.000

wait-for-event
token-bucket-response
----

